Package: omnifocusR
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve Task and Project Data from your OmniFocus Database
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jacobo Blanco
Maintainer: Jacobo Blanco <jayb88@gmail.com>
Description: Extracts task information from the 'OmniFocus' to-do application into tidy
    data frames for analysis and visualizationg. 'OmnifocusR' parses JSON files
    generated by 'OmniFocus' to create a single data frame containing task information,
    such as project name, related tags, start and end dates, and more.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports:
  dplyr,
  tidyr,
  xml2,
  lubridate,
  tibble,
  rlang
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    covr
Encoding: UTF-8
